BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:8w5gPPUQr23nllRJKxPky
SUMMARY:Chamber 101 - A Free Comprehensive Introduction to Chamber Membersh
	ip
DTSTAMP:20260405T040306Z
DTSTART:20260408T223000Z
DESCRIPTION:Chamber 101: An Introduction to the Seattle Southside Chamber o
	f Commerce led by Zak Nyberg and Andrea Jones. Join us for an introductory
	 session designed to help new\, prospective\, and existing members better 
	understand the role of the Chamber and how it supports businesses in the S
	outhside community. Attendees will learn about the Chamber team\, membersh
	ip benefits\, key programs\, and practical ways to maximize their engageme
	nt while connecting with other local businesses. During this event\, atten
	dees will learn: What a Chamber of Commerce is and the role it plays in st
	rengthening the local business ecosystem. What our Chamber is\, including 
	an introduction of each team member\, an overview of our mission in the So
	uthside\, and the various programs we support How membership works\, what 
	benefits are available\, including free with membership and affordable opt
	ions\, and how to make the most of the resources\, programs\, and visibili
	ty opportunities offered. Ways to get involved\, from attending events and
	 committees to leveraging promotional tools and support services. Chamber 
	101 is ideal for anyone looking to better understand how the Chamber suppo
	rts business success and how to fully engage with its mission and network 
	for your ROI. This is great for new and existing members\, as well as anyo
	ne interested in joining the Seattle Southside Chamber. This session provi
	des a welcoming space to ask questions\, meet Chamber staff\, and connect 
	with fellow community members. FREE to register\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcit
	y.com/events/#/details/chamber-101-a-free-comprehensive-introduction-to-ch
	amber-membership/18505171/2026-04-08T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Learning & Educ
	ation
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/chamber-101-a-free-compre
	hensive-introduction-to-chamber-membership/18505171/2026-04-08T00
LOCATION:Chamber Office\, 3100 S 176th St\, SeaTac\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-learning
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Learning & Education
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H30M
END:VEVENT
